《'''日滿議定書'''》是在[[滿洲國|滿洲國]][[大同_(满洲国)|大同]]元年（1932年，[[昭和|昭和]]七年）9月15日由[[大日本帝國|大日本帝國]]與[[滿洲國|滿洲國]]簽訂的[[条约|議定書]]。日本於1931年{{tsl|en|Japanese invasion of Manchuria|入侵滿洲}}，再於1932年3月1日成立滿洲國，最終於本條約中承認它。條約亦包括一共同防衛協議，容許日本於滿洲國領土駐兵<ref>"The protocol specified a mutual defence arrangement between Japan and Manchukuo and an unconditional stationing of Japanese troops, thereby justifying Japan's occupation of Manchuria and Japan's expanding aggression." in [https://books.google.com/books?id=Q4pX1uKkWf8C&pg=PA20 ''Continent, coast, ocean: dynamics of regionalism in Eastern Asia'' by Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia. Institut Alam dan Tamadun Melayu,Institute of Southeast Asian Studies p.20] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Q4pX1uKkWf8C&pg=PA20 |date=20201215043821 }}</ref>。

日本代表是陸軍大將[[武藤信義|武藤信義]]（[[關東軍|關東軍]]司令官），[[滿洲國|滿洲國]]代表則是國務總理[[鄭孝胥|鄭孝胥]]。雙方於[[新京|新京]]簽字於上，彼此享以[[香檳酒|香檳酒]]，完成手續。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Q4pX1uKkWf8C&pg=PA20|publisher=Institute of Southeast Asian Studies|date=2007-05-22|isbn=9789812304483|language=en|first=Ooi Kee|last=Beng|first2=Ding Choo|last2=Ming|title=Continent, Coast, Ocean: Dynamics of Regionalism in Eastern Asia|pages=20|access-date=2017-12-27|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215043821/https://books.google.com/books?id=Q4pX1uKkWf8C&pg=PA20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 內容 ==
* 日本'''承認滿洲國'''
* 滿洲國領土由日本和滿洲共同防衛

==結果==
使得[[滿洲|滿洲]]徹底的變相淪為了日本[[殖民地|殖民地]]，[[滿洲國|滿洲國]]成為了對日本[[關東軍|關東軍]]軍部的[[傀儡政權|傀儡政權]]。

